Missing features
----------------

Option to cancel sieving in PrimeSieve and ParallelPrimeSieve objects.

OpenMP
------

1. Make ParallelPrimeSieve.cpp exception safe once OpenMP supports
   C++ exceptions.
2. Test if the new OpenMP 4.0 affinity() clause speeds up primesieve.
3. Once OpenMP supports array reduction I should use it in
   ParallelPrimeSieve.cpp.

